{"id": "1399296113193914368", "channel_id": "1398620009898708992", "type": 19, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "我問號是因為你連星辰篇埋骨原本機制都搞錯了，照你的說法這次的更新的效果不會改變到東西\n\n我一開始說了原先就是扣除後，進場才+25%(這部分敘述是關卡開始+25%\n並且說明有測試過 (當然有些情況四埋骨可能基礎死抗超過400%扣除量會有差異\n\n所以我才說改機制是改這樣，你的結論都相反了為何會覺得你推導過程一樣", "timestamp": "2025-07-28T07:43:11.050000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": ["456226577798135808"], "reactions": [], "attachments": [{"id": "1399296112627679342", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 25950, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1398620009898708992/1399296112627679342/image.png?ex=69cccc8e&is=69cb7b0e&hm=c346762a77e0ba723e68b8cbe0ef90f90b22a39f28fa0e2e76233942360df9aa&"}, {"id": "1399296112967290961", "filename": "image.png", "content_type": "image/png", "size": 20933, "url": "https://cdn.discordapp.com/attachments/1398620009898708992/1399296112967290961/image.png?ex=69cccc8e&is=69cb7b0e&hm=41a6597d8da0a753c203f11c057d08202efb8d64caa571ac90849999584d943c&"}], "embeds": [], "reply_to": "1399259150139260939", "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1398620009898708992", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.3.0.2 在线维护公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080", "1361342543970697397"]}
{"id": "1399297383849791569", "channel_id": "1398620009898708992", "type": 0, "author_id": "655338276554801152", "author_name": "arr5721", "author_bot": false, "content": "然後我說星辰篇後很長一段時間是因為我除了剛改版那段時間外沒對星辰篇的死抗做紀錄\n所以一開始是以為你說的是正確的，想說會不會是出bug導致機制改變，今天改回最開始星辰篇樣子\n只是結果是你也沒測而已", "timestamp": "2025-07-28T07:48:13.998000+00:00", "edited_timestamp": null, "pinned": false, "mentions": [], "reactions": [], "attachments": [], "embeds": [], "reply_to": null, "has_thread": false, "thread_id": "1398620009898708992", "flags": 0, "thread_title": "V2.3.0.2 在线维护公告", "forum_channel_id": "1181135756958371881", "thread_tags": ["1181135885849346080", "1361342543970697397"]}
